The year is 2025, and following a nuclear disaster at the Springfield Nuclear Power Plant, thousands of apes enter the plant to take care of the clean up. Days later, the Apes emerge from the plant completely transformed into Humanoid Chimps. Immune to radiation, they now inhabit the abandoned town of Springfield.
